00:27:28,780 --> 00:27:30,040
if anything occurs to you later.

569
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:32,721
I field questions from people in industry

570
00:27:32,761 --> 00:27:34,642
about what it's like in academia all the time,

571
00:27:35,062 --> 00:27:37,302
but I can also take some questions.

